": \"I said, 'If Snoop can carry the torch in Paris - come on, man - Flav can carry that bad boy in LA!'\\\"\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999719541397, \"rank\": 2.804592623714824e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop's impressive stint as torchbearer also influenced Flavor's decision.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Praising Snoop's performance, Flavor said, \\\"Snoop did a fantastic job, man.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He rocked.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though they did pay him a half-a-million a day, Snoop got a nice payday out there, besides the payday, he did a good job and I know that man had a lot of fun out there.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mad big ups to you, Snoop.\\\"\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At 65, Flavor Flav's enthusiasm remains undiminished, and he sees the torch relay as a significant opportunity to contribute to an iconic event in his home country.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6558911203780266e-34, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One specific aspiration for Flavor Flav is to earn a custom Olympic pin, much like Snoop did.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6558911203780266e-34, \"text\": \"Flavor Flav\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flavor_Flav\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This small but symbolic token seems to have added to his determination to succeed.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want one of them pins too.\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1892, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He got his own Olympic pin.\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am gonna try to get me one of them Olympic pins,\\\" Flav said.\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 AllHipHop.com LLC 2025-Infinity\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": []}]}"